          //PolyU (ExprAn, ExprAn-1, ExprAn-2,...,ExprA0,VarExpr);   ExprAn, ExprAn-1, ExprAn-2,...,ExprA0- Any Type: Real&Complex; VarExpr- Any Type;
          {
