//so as (2*x*y+1)^(2*x*y+1) many much  than (2*x*y+1)*(3*x*t+1)

endp:
//sin(z1)-sin(z1/z2)
//sin(x)-sin(z1)

//sin(x)-cos(z1)
//sqr(z1)-x^y
//sqr(z1)-z1^z2
